      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Explore the Jakarta AQuarium Safari and witness 3500 species of aquatic and non-aquatic animals. You will see various marine animals, and the aquarium also offers educational information with expert guides. Children can participate in drawing activities to enhance their creativity, and there are many other exciting attractions to enjoy. It's an ideal tourist destination for families with children, who will surely enjoy their visit."
          }
